(171,'Gana Art Center','https://english.visitseoul.net/attractions/Gana-Art-Center/ENP002082','The Gana Art Center is a multipurpose art space that holds exhibitions, performances, classes, and auctions. The sprawling center was designed by the world-renowned architect Jean Michel Wilmotte. The Gana Art Center operates a convenient shuttle bus for visitors. The shuttle bus runs every day except Mondays and national holidays.','-1660','Tue-Sun 10:00 - 19:00 KST','Mondays','03004  28, Pyeongchang 30-gil, Jongno-gu, Seoul','Subway Line 5 Gwanghwamun Station Exit 2 / Subway Line 3 Gyeongbokgung Station Exit 3, take bus 1020 or 1711 and get off at Lotte Apartment, 150m','https://english.visitseoul.net/comm/getImage?srvcId=MEDIA&parentSn=72857&fileTy=MEDIA&fileNo=1&thumbTy=L | https://english.visitseoul.net/comm/getImage?srvcId=MEDIA&parentSn=72858&fileTy=MEDIA&fileNo=1&thumbTy=L | https://english.visitseoul.net/comm/getImage?srvcId=MEDIA&parentSn=72859&fileTy=MEDIA&fileNo=1&thumbTy=L | https://english.visitseoul.net/comm/getImage?srvcId=MEDIA&parentSn=72860&fileTy=MEDIA&fileNo=1&thumbTy=L',4.000000,37.612212,'ENP002082'),
